2013?

4
00:00:48,150 --> 00:00:49,000
Bed three,

5
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:49,920
why are you out of bed?

6
00:00:49,920 --> 00:00:51,670
And why did you pull the IV out?

7
00:00:52,110 --> 00:00:53,430
The time's wrong, right?

8
00:00:53,640 --> 00:00:55,000
It should be 2013,

9
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:55,960
or 2023 now?

10
00:00:55,960 --> 00:00:57,280
What do you mean by 2023?

11
00:00:57,750 --> 00:00:59,430
How hard did you bang your head?

12
00:00:59,430 --> 00:01:00,240
How could it be 2023?

13
00:01:00,240 --> 00:01:00,960
It's 2023 now.

14
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:01,960
You're lying to me!

15
00:01:01,960 --> 00:01:02,880
You're trying to fool me, right?

16
00:01:02,880 --> 00:01:03,430
Help!

17
00:01:03,430 --> 00:01:04,790
You got the time wrong, didn't you?

18
00:01:04,790 --> 00:01:05,640
What are you doing?

19
00:01:06,310 --> 00:01:07,120
Don't touch me!

20
00:01:07,120 --> 00:01:08,150
Let me go! Let me go!

21
00:01:08,150 --> 00:01:08,870
Let go!

22
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:14,480
Dad, Brother,

23
00:01:17,790 --> 00:01:18,640
you two…

24
00:01:18,790 --> 00:01:20,280
You look so young!

25
