44
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:09,000
He disguised himself as the Captain
of Dark Dragon Guard

45
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:10,310
to destroy our Feng Family!

46
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:12,030
Dad.

47
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:14,400
Starting tomorrow,

48
00:02:14,470 --> 00:02:16,030
