55
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:26,430
Dad! Dad!

56
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,400
Brother, you believe me, right?

57
00:02:32,630 --> 00:02:33,430
Zhengnan,

58
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:35,630
