62
00:02:41,310 --> 00:02:42,800
Report to the Group tomorrow.

63
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,870
Don't worry about performance.

64
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,470
Just concentrate on getting better.

65
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:51,680
Brother.

66
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:51,960
Lin Rui,

67
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:52,520
