73
00:03:18,750 --> 00:03:20,590
Jingqing should be in Grade 12

74
00:03:23,310 --> 00:03:25,310
and Meng Fan is also a high schooler.

75
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:38,470
Hello,

76
00:03:39,590 --> 00:03:40,430
Jingqing…

77
00:03:46,160 --> 00:03:48,480
[91 Days to College Entrance Examination]

78
00:03:48,910 --> 00:03:50,030
I remember Mo

79
00:03:50,030 --> 00:03:52,430
jumped to her death two months
before the College Entrance Examination.

80
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:54,080
So that means

81
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,310
there's one month left.

82
00:03:58,280 --> 00:03:59,030
Mo.

83
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:01,470
What did you call me?

84
00:04:03,310 --> 00:04:04,630
A slip of the tongue. Sorry.

85
00:04:05,750 --> 00:04:07,240
Why did you hug me just now?

86
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:09,000
How do I explain this...

87
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,840
I had a weird dream.

88
00:04:18,390 --> 00:04:19,800
You dare touch my books?

89
00:04:20,310 --> 00:04:20,920
Don't move.

90
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:21,630
What's the deal?

91
00:04:22,950 --> 00:04:24,160
You wanna take advantage
of the school belle again?

92
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:24,950
Zhao Shuai!

93
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,040
Don't worry, babe.

94
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:27,950
I'll get back at him

95
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:29,240
for you.

96
00:04:30,950 --> 00:04:31,600
Babe,

97
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:32,430
