98
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:33,950
Fan, are you crazy?

99
00:04:33,950 --> 00:04:34,920
Let go of me!

100
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:35,750
Let me go!

101
00:04:35,750 --> 00:04:36,240
Fan! Fan!

102
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:36,720
You're Houzi.

103
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:37,430
Let go of me.

104
00:04:37,430 --> 00:04:38,070
Listen to me.

105
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:39,070
Well, Zhao Shuai,

106
00:04:39,070 --> 00:04:39,830
we're all classmates.

107
00:04:39,830 --> 00:04:40,830
Let's talk it out.

108
00:04:47,390 --> 00:04:48,600
Boss! Boss!

109
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:51,070
Are you okay?

110
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:52,510
I'm fine. Let's go!

111
00:04:52,510 --> 00:04:53,240
Let's go!

112
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:56,120
Stop right there!

113
00:05:00,510 --> 00:05:01,430
Fan, go!

114
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:02,310
Go!

115
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:03,800
