116
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:04,510
Boss!

117
00:05:04,630 --> 00:05:05,310
Chase them! Go!

118
00:05:05,310 --> 00:05:06,430
Boss, are you okay?

119
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:16,830
Why are you rushing?

120
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:21,310
You're too fat.

121
