You need to train more.

122
00:05:22,270 --> 00:05:23,040
Hey.

123
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:25,120
What are you planning?

124
00:05:25,430 --> 00:05:26,920
Transfer schools

125
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:27,920
