126
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:30,120
No transferring or dropping out.

127
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,480
Then what's your plan?

128
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,310
Listen,

129
00:05:32,310 --> 00:05:33,390
