130
00:05:33,390 --> 00:05:34,800
in front of Mr. Wong,

131
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:36,430
and now you even hit Zhao Shuai?

132
00:05:36,950 --> 00:05:37,800
Who did this?

133
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,310
Who else?

134
00:05:39,310 --> 00:05:40,830
This happens every day.

135
00:05:41,310 --> 00:05:42,630
Come on, hop on my bike.

136
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:49,560
Is this Zhao Shuai's?

137
00:05:49,870 --> 00:05:50,870
This bike is worth thousands.

138
00:05:50,870 --> 00:05:52,430
Only he can afford it.

139
00:05:54,070 --> 00:05:55,600
Don't do anything stupid.

140
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:57,630
One tire of it costs more
than our lives combined.

141
00:05:58,390 --> 00:06:00,390
Are our lives really that cheap?

142
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,240
Well, that's hard to say.

143
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:03,000
Get lost.

144
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,040
What are you up to?

145
00:06:07,750 --> 00:06:09,310
You think you're a master thief?

146
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:11,510
Stop messing around.

147
00:06:11,510 --> 00:06:12,750
Just hop on my bike.

148
00:06:12,750 --> 00:06:13,600
If Zhao Shuai catches us,

149
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:15,040
we're done for.

150
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,120
Oh, my!

151
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:19,510
You really got it open!

152
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:20,680
When did you learn this?

153
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:21,630
Why didn't I know?

154
00:06:23,430 --> 00:06:24,040
I...

155
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:24,720
Move aside.

156
00:06:25,830 --> 00:06:26,920
Wait for me! Let's go together!

157
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:28,920
Chase them!

158
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:29,360
Stop!

159
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:30,120
Stop!

160
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:31,070
Hurry up, chase them!

161
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:33,480
Wait.

162
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:34,430
Oh no!

163
00:06:34,430 --> 00:06:36,310
Where's my bike?

164
00:06:36,510 --> 00:06:37,310
Boss,

165
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:39,390
Meng Fan's bike is still here.

166
00:06:39,390 --> 00:06:40,430
So that means

167
00:06:40,950 --> 00:06:42,310
he's riding

168
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:44,070
your bike, Boss!

169
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:49,430
Meng Fan, you're dead!

170
00:06:50,510 --> 00:06:51,680
All happy and cheerful.

171
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:52,390
Watch out!

172
00:06:56,950 --> 00:06:58,800
Based on what you said,

173
00:06:58,870 --> 00:07:00,430
you had cancer,

174
00:07:00,750 --> 00:07:02,600
died a year later,

175
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,950
and then got reborn

176
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:05,750
to the day of your diagnosis.

177
00:07:06,510 --> 00:07:07,510
Since then,

178
00:07:07,510 --> 00:07:08,800
every time you die,

179
00:07:08,830 --> 00:07:09,950
you are reborn

180
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:12,000
and repeat this,

181
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:13,310
endlessly looping.

182
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,000
It's happened

183
00:07:17,070 --> 00:07:18,680
1,000 times now.

184
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:21,950
You're Emperor Qing.

185
00:07:24,270 --> 00:07:25,240
